title: My 10 Books - September 2015 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 books for this month, 4 PDFs and 6 ePUBs:

01. A Brief History of Numbers - Leo Corry
02. The Medieval Manuscript Book - Cultural Approaches
03. The Story of Helium and the Birth of Astrophysics
04. Behind Every Great Man - The Forgotten Women Behind the World's Famous and Infamous
05. Just In Time Algebra - Colleen Schultz
06. The Quantum Dissidents - Rebuilding the Foundations of Quantum Mechanics
07. The Book of Ancient Bastards - Brian Thornton
08. Great Calculations - A Surprising Look Behind 50 Scientific Inquiries
09. Football's Strangest Matches - Extraordinary But True Stories from Over a Century of Football
10. The Encyclopedia of World Ballet - Mary Ellen Snodgrass
